<table border="0" width="100%" id="table16" cellpadding="0">
	<tr>
		<td style="font-family: Trebuchet MS; font-size: 8pt; color: #FFFFFF; font-weight: bold; text-align: left; background-color: #333333; border-left: 2px solid #000000; border-right: 2px solid #FFFFFF; border-top: 2px solid #000000; border-bottom: 2px solid #FFFFFF">
          		<br><u><i><font color="#FFFF00">MISC CODES:</font></i></u><br>
			&nbsp; Hidden Teams -
                  &nbsp; <font color="#00FF00">Left, Right, Up, Down, R1, L1, Square, Down, after you hear the buzzer press Left, Right, Up, Down, R1, L1, Square, Up</font>&nbsp;
				  <br>&nbsp; Big head mode -
                  &nbsp; <font color="#00FF00">Select the teams and go to the scouting report screens. Highlight the ''Continue'' option on the second scouting report screen and press X. Immediately tap L1 repeatedly until tip off. During the game, press Start to pause, then Start again to resume</font>&nbsp;
				  <br>&nbsp; Shot % Indicator -
                  &nbsp; <font color="#00FF00">Go to the second scouting report screen, highlight ''continue'', and press X or start; as the screen disappears, immediately hold the L1 button untill the tip-off. After the tip-off, press the start button to pause. Unpause and whenever a player takes a shot an on screen percent indicator will show how likely the player will make the shot.</font>&nbsp;
				  <br>&nbsp; Small Player Mode -
                  &nbsp; <font color="#00FF00">Go to the second scouting report screen, highlight ''continue'' and press X or start; as the screen dissappears, immediately tap the R1 button and repeat untill tip-off. After the tip-off, press start to pause and when you unpause, all of the players will be tiny.</font>&nbsp;<br>
				  <br><u><i><font color="#FFFF00">ACTION REPLAY CODES:</font></i></u><br>
			&nbsp; Home team score modifier (?0000-FFFF) -
                  &nbsp; <font color="#00FF00"><br>800ED9A0 ????</font>&nbsp;
				  <br>&nbsp; Away team score modifier (?0000-FFFF) -
                  &nbsp; <font color="#00FF00"><br>800EDB84 ????</font>&nbsp;<br><br>
	 </tr>
	</table>
